This class manages a meeting recording session or a meeting replay.

uploadAllFiles

public void uploadAllFiles(java.lang.String sFilePath,
                           java.lang.String sMeetingID)
                    throws java.lang.Exception
Upload file of n3 data with the given name to the triplestore. And the zip with the xml and references to the appropriate place. If upload appears successful, tag the files as uploaded by renaming file with '.uploaded' at the end. If renaming the files is not successful, delete the n3 file. We do not want to upload the same file twice as this will over-populate the elements of triplestore data for this meeting.

Parameters:
sFilePath - the file of data to upload..
sMeetingID - the id of the meeting to upload all files for.
Throws:
java.lang.Exception - if something goes wrong with either upload.
